 497:Drivers/lvgl/src/font/fmt_txt/lv_font_fmt_txt.c **** /**
 498:Drivers/lvgl/src/font/fmt_txt/lv_font_fmt_txt.c ****  * Read bits from an input buffer. The read can cross byte boundary.
 499:Drivers/lvgl/src/font/fmt_txt/lv_font_fmt_txt.c ****  * @param in the input buffer to read from.
